online\/2012\/08\/29\/supplication-in-witr-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":31728,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet\u2019s supplication in Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when he finished his Witr prayer with invocations of peace, he would say, \u201cGlory to the King, the Holy.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1430 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4437,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/end-salat-salaam-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31728,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet ends prayer with peace, mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Wa\u2019il ibn Hujr reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he would end by invoking peace on his right side, saying, \u201cPeace be upon you, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings,\u201d and again to his left side, saying, \u201cPeace and mercy of Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/24\/allah-faces-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":31728,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Allah faces him in prayer unless he looks elsewhere","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty continues to face towards the servant while he is in prayer as long as he does not avert his eyes. If he looks elsewhere, Allah will turn elsewhere.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 909 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31747,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/in-salat-waiting-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":31728,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: You are in prayer if you are waiting for prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: We prayed with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, at nightfall and he did not come out until half of the night had passed. The Prophet said, \u201cTake your places.\u201d We took our places and the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, people have prayed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41157,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/08\/reward-intending-mosque\/","url_meta":{"origin":31728,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jama\u2019ah: Reward for intending congregational prayer, even if missed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution in the best manner, then sets out but finds that the people had already prayed, then Allah Almighty will give him the reward of its prayer and its attendance without detracting from their\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33970,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/05\/o-bilal-comfort-us-with-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":31728,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: O Bilal, comfort us with the prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Muhammad reported: The time for prayer arrived, and he said to some of his relatives, \u201cYoung lady, bring me water for ablution that I might pray and be comforted.\u201d We objected to that from him, but he said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/31728","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"hr